# Privacy Policy
Effective date: April 14, 2019

Classic Copter is a fun game application.

This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.

## Information Collection And Use
We do not collect any kind of data. The application simply connects you to your google play account for leaderboard and achievement list. No user profile or data is used in any form by me. 

